songs.title: Fāār-i-kāāl (Charli XCX Remix)
songs.lyrics:
This feels wrong
But let’s go
Our bones are sinking
Deep into the ocean

This feels wrong
But let’s go
We’re drowning in the
Flames of our devotion

I can’t feel it
‘Cause I’ve just thrown it
In the waves

I can’t feel it
Won’t you just save me?
OH!
